         <p class="breadcrumbs">You are here: <a href="/en.html?id=4">Government.no</a> / <a href="/en/dep/fad.html?id=339">Ministry of Government Admi...</a> / <a href="/en/dep/fad/Selected-topics.html?id=341">Selected topics</a> / <span>National minorities</span>
